-- Exxon raises second-quarter dividend 14 percent
-- 
-- Wed Apr 30, 2008 1:42pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/30/us-exxon-dividend-idUSWEN535320080430

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Exxon Mobil Corp on Wednesday said it will raise its second quarter dividend 14 percent to 40 cents a share. 

 The company said the dividend will be payable on June 10 to shareholders of record on May 13. Its first quarter dividend was 35 cents a share. (Reporting by  Michael Erman )